  "Description": {
    "English": "A slab of seafood, created in the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Nutrient Processor</span>. Food such as this can be <span class=\"name name-stellar\">highly valuable</span>.<br><br>Can be consumed as it stands or subjected to further processing.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "在<span class=\"name name-technology\">营养处理器</span>中创造的大份海鲜。此类食物拥有<span class=\"name name-stellar\">极高的价值</span>。<br><br>能够直接食用或者进一步加工。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">營養處理器</span>製成的一塊海鮮肉排。這種食物可能具有<span class=\"name name-stellar\">高度價值</span>。<br><br>可直接食用或進一步加工。"
  },
